{"tid":158421,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"搭巴士隔離坐肥婆定後面坐頂頂人慘d?","createTime":"2017-03-16T09:04:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-07T15:41:47.000Z","uid":13652,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c47e5bec25f8733e7a3981f9f0b201509cf73966","tid":158421,"uid":13652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T09:04:49.000Z","msg":"明明有走廊位唔坐<br />\n個肥婆係要zip入黎坐窗口位<br />\n一野坐鳩左個半位<br />\n入黎果時仲要踩我一腳<br />\n唔係歧視肥婆<br />\n但你可唔可以坐走廊位<br />\n突自己個半個蘿由出去而唔係我果半個呢<br />\n<br />\n永遠後面個人都係頂頂下<br />\n我知你腳長<br />\n但你一係就頂實<br />\n唔好郁黎郁去丫<br />\n頂下頂下咁好撚辛苦呀<br />\n<br />\n究竟邊樣慘d <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我而家最慘 同時發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"456cec179cd294ab49e5c6a6d0499333f88569a1","tid":158421,"uid":44333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T09:08:25.000Z","msg":"坐肥婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dff1d7f4194efdde4481bc1ef79b6031ceee69de","tid":158421,"uid":48834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T09:09:57.000Z","msg":"坐對面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唯有盤坐"},{"pid":"a930a015363389de6cbb97061b0a5393955eaf61","tid":158421,"uid":10992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T09:13:45.000Z","msg":"坐肥婆上面"},{"pid":"664f50dfdfff9813fd151be8d9f2ee3a3262a8d6","tid":158421,"uid":74262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T09:14:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"67d8eaf90c921b60ef8cf91ca8a8a3cf0f8a79dd","tid":158421,"uid":13652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T09:18:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你唔撚識轉位架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？<br />\n有唔中意既人坐我隔離我即刻起身坐去前面</blockquote><br />\n肥婆係上公路前尾站先上<br />\n已經冇哂位<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm